Source URLs:
- https://axios-http.com/docs/handling_errors
- https://axios-http.com/docs/cancellation
Fetched: 2026-02-27

Axios best-practice notes:
- Classify error.response vs error.request vs setup errors.
- Use validateStatus when custom HTTP acceptance is required.
- Use timeout + AbortController signal for robust cancellation coverage.
- Use error.toJSON() for richer diagnostics.

Implementation implications:
- Preserve structured provider error extraction.
- Keep explicit timeout and categorized retryability.
